  ('dietitian-moex-05229', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種病歷紀錄格式最不適合臨床營養照顧使用？', '["Subjective,Objective,Assessment,Plan（SOAP）", "Problem-OrientedMedicalRecords（POMR）", "HazardAnalysisCriticalControlPoints（HACCP）", "Assessment,Diagnosis,Intervention,Monitoring,Evaluation（ADIME）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbf6ab0762fa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8f6714688dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05230', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '篩檢病人營養不良MalnutritionUniversalScreeningTool（MUST）量表的項目，不包括下列何者？', '["急性疾病影響攝食的狀態", "身體質量指數", "小腿圍", "非計畫性體重喪失"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbf6ab0762fa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8f6714688dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05231', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳先生73歲，教育程度為高中畢業，因肺炎合併急性呼吸衰竭住院。病人雖可以進食但食量少， 為了解其正確的進食量，應該使用何種飲食評估方法較理想？', '["飲食記錄", "飲食頻率", "24小時回憶法", "飲食史"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbf6ab0762fa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8f6714688dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05232', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '鼻胃管灌食的重症病人，下列何者不是降低aspiration風險的最佳處置？', '["檢查胃殘餘量", "抬高頭部", "持續會厭下抽痰（continuoussubglotticsuctioning）", "口腔清潔（oraldecontamination）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbf6ab0762fa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8f6714688dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05233', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關再餵食症候群（refeedingsyndrome）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["原先營養狀態正常的嚴重外傷病人因病情及手術導致過去兩週幾無營養攝入，在開始灌食時也 屬高風險族群", "特別容易出現在接受高脂肪高熱量飲食的病人", "典型的表現為「三低一高」，包括低血磷、低血鉀、低血糖及高血鎂", "若發生再餵食症候群時，建議加快腸道或靜脈營養的給予速度，以矯正營養素的缺乏"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbf6ab0762fa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8f6714688dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
